What if, before she died, she wrote a letter
saying she chose Harvey Den
t over you? And what if, to spare you pain,
I burnt that letter?It's not just your name, sir.
It's your father's name. And it's all that's left
of him. Don't destroy it.aybe someday, when
Gotham no longer needs Batman I'll see
him again.
